data.description: Welcome to an exceptional investment opportunity in San Bernardino! This well-maintained duplex, strategically located at 805 W 7th St and 674 N H St. Additionally, a third unit, converted from a garage at 674 N H St, adds to the property's appeal.    Currently, all units are rented out, generating a total monthly income of $6,100. The tenants at 805 W 7th St, a spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom unit, cover all utilities, contributing to a positive cash flow. Meanwhile, the units at 674 N H St and 674 1/2 N H St have the owner covering the utility expenses.    Investors will find this property particularly enticing due to its attractive cash flow, even with a minimal down payment. Alternatively, for a buyer looking to reside in one unit while managing the others, this duplex is an ideal fit.    The meticulous care given to the property is evident in the recent upgrades. At 805 W 7th St, enjoy the benefits of new vinyl windows throughout, fully remodeled bathrooms, fresh LVP flooring in the kitchen, updated copper water lines from main line all the way to each faucet, ABS plumbing throughout all the way to curb line, a new wood fence surrounding the corner lot, lush St Augustine sod laid within the last 12 months, breaker upgrades, and new fans in every room. The landscaping, featuring river rock accents, enhances the overall aesthetic appeal.    674 N H St boasts new PEX water lines from the property entrance to kitchen and bathroom faucets. Meanwhile, 674 1/2 N H St is entirely updated, featuring a recently installed mini-split system for added comfort. In each unit, tenants benefit from the convenience of provided washer and dryer facilities.    This property is not just a home; it's a smart investment opportunity with immediate returns and potential for future appreciation. Don't miss your chance to own a well-maintained duplex with a strong rental history in San Bernardino!    Drone Footage  https://drive.google.com/file/d/1CSu1uFCcKydnlGyg7COi9wkA0-H0oN0r/view
